components:

info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Spotify Spotify
  title: Spotify Spotify
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Spotify Add To Playlist
      parameters:
      - description: Search Query to pass to spotify
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Search Query
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Playlist ID to add to
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Playlist ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Will skip to the next song in the playlist
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Skip Current Playing Song (PREMIUM ONLY)
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Spotify Add to Playlist
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Spotify Add To Queue. Only works if you have Spotify Premium
      parameters:
      - description: Search Query to pass to spotify
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Search Query
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Will skip to the next song in the queue
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Skip Current Playing Song (PREMIUM ONLY)
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Spotify Add to Queue (PREMIUM ONLY)
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Spotify Resume Playback. Only works if you have Spotify Premium
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Spotify Resume Playback (PREMIUM ONLY)
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: Spotify Skip a song in the playing queue. Only works if you have
        Spotify Premium
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp3'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Spotify Skip Song in Queue (PREMIUM ONLY)
tags:
- {name: Miscellaneous}
